{
  "text": "TerminoWeb is a bit more complex than systems such as WebCorp [CITATION_1] or KWiCFinder [CITATION_2] as it provides an integration of multiple modules, and therefore requires a longer learning curve, but the integration also makes it quite powerful, allowing a workflow such as described in this article, to start from a source text and find valuable information from the automatically extracted terms of that source text.",
  "citation_candidates": [
